N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 4604.1 - Application to amend

State Regulations

An application to amend a license shall be made to the
municipal governing body on form GC-6 "Application to Amend Games of Chance

License", as prescribed by the commission. Notes
